Megatron smiles and evil smile. He dosent need bright warrior, he's had
trouble with them in the past, "Well then, you are a welcome member in the
Decepticon ranks. Switchblade, show him around, Astroblast, you and the
other Decepticons finish moving these parts into the ship. I have an
apointment to attend to." he says as he head down towards Autofire.
